    "en": {
      "title": "1 Crore cash recovered by the protesters at the President's House",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "At the President's House, more than one crore rupees recovered by the protestors has been handed over to the police.",
        "The President's House located in the Colombo Fort was besieged by rioters after the people protested against the government on Saturday 9th yesterday.",
        "After this, the demonstrators who entered the Presidential Palace seized one crore 78 lakh 50 thousand rupees from a secret place of a room said to have been used by Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "In this case, after the protestors handed over the money to the Superintendent of Police who was in charge of duties in that area, the money was handed over to the Fort Police Station."
      ],
